    "In addition, China's rise as a global economic leader and its role in initiatives like the Belt and Road highlight its ascent (Tombari 2021; Zou et al. 2022).",
    "Positioned to become the world's largest economy, China's strategic initiatives, especially the Belt and Road, showcase its influence, shaping global trade, connectivity, and geopolitics significantly.",
